precis:
The transfer from the Secretary of State for External Affairs to the
Minister of COMMMUNICATIONS of the powers, duties and functions respecting
international expositions, AND the control and supervision of that portion
of the public service of Canada in the Department of External Affairs
known as the INTERNATIONAL EXPOSITIONS DIVISION.
